    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty! I have babied this car from day one, and it's still in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels just like new. It\u2019s super clean, looks stunning, and drives like an absolute dream. I'm really looking for a great new owner who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you're interested, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
