      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\udc4b Check out this absolute beauty! It\u2019s in seriously perfect shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it really shows in every detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels and drives just like new, this is definitely the one for you! Come see it for yourself, you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
