    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 high-revving inline-six, exhibiting perfect valve timing via a meticulously serviced Double-VANOS system. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed to the highest standard, including a subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement using VAC coated bearings. Power is managed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-Differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a suspension overhaul using OEM bushings to preserve the original kinematics. With a paint-meter-verified finish and a clinically clean undercarriage, this M3 represents a superlative example of the marque\u2019s engineering peak.",
